sequenceDiagram
    participant Client as SDK / Client
    participant API as Sandbox API
    participant Orchestrator as Orchestrator
    participant FC as Firecracker VM

    Client->>API: create(template, timeout, autoPause)
    API->>Orchestrator: 启动或恢复 VM
    Orchestrator->>FC: start / restore
    FC-->>Client: running sandbox

    Client->>API: pause(sandboxId)
    API->>Orchestrator: 触发暂停
    Orchestrator->>FC: pause / snapshot
    FC-->>API: state=paused

    Client->>API: connect(sandboxId, timeout)
    API->>Orchestrator: resume if paused + extend TTL
    Orchestrator->>FC: resume
    FC-->>Client: running sandbox
